Orochimaru's Training
Goal: To Know Every Jutsu in the World and even those Jutsu yet to be discovered. 

Get the Cursed Seal of Heaven placed on you and Survive. 
Take the Awakening Pill and advance to Stage 2 Cursed Seal of Heaven. 
Use Forbidden Jutsu and even Medical Enhancement.

Use Chidori to cut through 4 Wooden Dummies. 

Immortality Jutsu:
You find a body, a young body pour your Spirit into it and make it your own. 

